summary: Makes Rabbits into cute Black rabbits. Easier to see in the snow, but they are cuter :D
descriptionHtml:
[size=10]Please NOTE I have moved the Max Res textures to another page which can be found here:

[url]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4033[/url]

They include more shades and variations on the HD texture [/size]

To install:

Place texture folder into your data folder:

\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data

This is my first mod, so hope you like it :D

PLEASE NOTE: higher resolution textures require higher system requirements then the vanilla game. Please ensure you have adequete hardware to run modifications which deviate from the standard texture sizes. 

Changelog

v1.0 - Standard sized texture, black rabbit

v1.2 - Higher resolution texture, slight alterations, black rabbit

v1.3 - (See main pic) Very high resolution texture (400% bigger), completely new texture using high res photographic shots. 

Note: You may use this texture for your own HD animal packs or whatever, give credit, thats all I need. Cheers!

Source animal:

[img]http://static.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/images/3134-1-1324227119.jpg[/img]
